---------How to run the code and Structure of the program---------

1) Folder Structure :-
calculator_project
│
│ cal.py
│
└── templates
      │ index.html
The templates folder is very important for Flask.

2) Open Terminal / Command Prompt :-
cd calculator_project

3) Install Flask (if not installed) :-
pip install flask

4) Run the Python file :-
python cal.py

5) Open the Website :-
After running, you will see something like:
Running on http://127.0.0.1:5000
Open your browser and go to:
http://127.0.0.1:5000
Your calculator website will open.
